);

alter table Common_employee add constraint FK_COMMON_E_REFERENCE_MANAGER foreign key (Leader_id)
references manager (employee_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table Common_employee add constraint "FK_COMMON_E_普通员工-员工_EMPLOYEE" foreign key (employee_id)
references employee (employee_id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
